ObjectStates.Name: Notecard
ObjectStates.Description:
- Choose COG Characters - Each player chooses which COG character they will play and takes both the figurine and player card as well as the starting weapon cards and ammo / grenade tokens

- Once you have the cards in your play area, you will need to properly distribute the ammo / grenade tokens based on your character card. -Proceed to Setup - Step 3...

ObjectStates.Name: Notecard
ObjectStates.Description:
- Shuffel both the Order Cards Deck and the Random Weapon Cards Deck below. They have already been placed on the appropiate space on the Mission Reference Sheet.

- Choose a mission and place the cards on the Mission Deck space on the Mission Reference Sheet below. Proceed to Setup - Step 5...

ObjectStates.Name: Notecard
ObjectStates.Description:
- Based on mission chosen, take the ALL appropiate Locust figures, cards, & wound tokens for each.
*Note- figurine and wound tokens outside of the bag are EXAMPLES only. Ticker doesn't have wound tokens & Berserker only has one wound token.
- Place the Locust card on the appropiate spot of the Mission Reference Sheet as desribed by Mission Setup card. Proceed to Setup - Step 5B...

ObjectStates.Name: Notecard
ObjectStates.Description:
- Setup Location deck and pull tiles based on chosen mission. For each "level" create a seperate deck as described on mission card and SHUFFLE each deck.  
Level 1 deck and tiles will be set aside for the next step. While, if applicable, Level 2 and Level 3 Decks will be placed on the appropiate spaces of the Mission Reference Sheet. Making note of any locked levels. 
Proceed to Setup - Step 7...

ObjectStates.Name: Notecard
ObjectStates.Description:
- Proceed in setting up the level 1 of the map. 
- Draw first card from created level 1 location deck and grab the appropiate tile.
-Spawn the Locust figures based on the botton of the location card drawn
-Continue this process for each location card in the level 1 deck. Last card drawn will have a door at the exit. 
-Proceed to Setup - Step 8

ObjectStates.Name: Notecard
ObjectStates.Description:
-Create enemy AI deck
-Pull each General AI cards listed in the mission setup.
-Pull ALL 4 cards for EACH enemy type listed in the mission setup. 
-Combine all of these cards and shuffle together and place the newly created deck in the appropiate space on the Mission Reference Sheet. 
-Proceed to Setup - Step 6...

ObjectStates.Name: Notecard
ObjectStates.Description:
- Place each players' figure on the first tile placed. ONE player has the option of going into a cover space on the first area when placing their figure.
-Each player draws their hand of Order Cards from the deck on the Mission Reference Sheet.
-You are now ready to  start playing the game! Refer to Player Turn Reference Card
